### ============================================
### HOTELS & ROOMS — All API Requests
### Base URL: change if your app runs on another port
### ============================================
@base = https://localhost:5091
# @base = http://localhost:5091

### ---------- PUBLIC: Hotels ----------

### 1) Search Hotels (no filters)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/hotels
Accept: application/json

### 2) Search Hotels (with query params)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/hotels?City=Cairo&PageNumber=1&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 3) Search Hotels (with dates & price)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/hotels?City=Cairo&CheckIn=2026-03-01&CheckOut=2026-03-05&MinPrice=50&MaxPrice=200&Stars=4&PageNumber=1&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 4) Search Hotels (geo radius — optional)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/hotels?Latitude=30.0444&Longitude=31.2357&RadiusInKm=10&PageNumber=1&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 5) Get Hotel Details (replace {hotel-id} with real GUID)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/hotels/REPLACE_WITH_HOTEL_ID
Accept: application/json

### 6) Get Hotel Rooms (no dates)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/hotels/REPLACE_WITH_HOTEL_ID/rooms
Accept: application/json

### 7) Get Hotel Rooms (with check-in/check-out for availability & total price)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/hotels/REPLACE_WITH_HOTEL_ID/rooms?checkin=2026-03-01&checkout=2026-03-05
Accept: application/json

### 8) Add Review (replace ids; Rating 1–5)
POST {{base}}/api/v1/hotels/REPLACE_WITH_HOTEL_ID/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hotelId": "REPLACE_WITH_HOTEL_ID",
  "userId": "REPLACE_WITH_USER_ID",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Great stay!"
}

###

