### ---------- ADMIN: Rooms ----------

### 11) Add Room (replace {hotelId} with hotel GUID)
POST {{base}}/api/v1/admin/hotels/REPLACE_WITH_HOTEL_ID/rooms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hotelId": "REPLACE_WITH_HOTEL_ID",
  "roomNumber": "101",
  "name": "Standard Double",
  "description": "Comfortable double room with view.",
  "basePricePerNight": 99.99,
  "photos": [
    { "url": "https://example.com/room1.jpg", "alt": "Room 101" }
  ]
}

###

### 12) Edit Room (replace {id} with room GUID)
PUT {{base}}/api/v1/admin/rooms/REPLACE_WITH_ROOM_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "REPLACE_WITH_ROOM_ID",
  "name": "Standard Double (Updated)",
  "description": "Updated description.",
  "basePricePerNight": 119.99
}

###

### 13) Set Room Availability (replace {id} with room GUID)
PUT {{base}}/api/v1/admin/rooms/REPLACE_WITH_ROOM_ID/availability
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": "REPLACE_WITH_ROOM_ID",
  "startDate": "2026-03-01",
  "endDate": "2026-03-31",
  "isAvailable": true
}

###

### 14) Add Seasonal Pricing (replace {id} with room GUID)
POST {{base}}/api/v1/admin/rooms/REPLACE_WITH_ROOM_ID/seasonal-pricing
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": "REPLACE_WITH_ROOM_ID",
  "startDate": "2026-06-01",
  "endDate": "2026-08-31",
  "price": 149.99
}

